::Zardus::

"I see..." Zardus says, looking at Nemesis and then down at Wolfgang.

"Take him back to base. I need some answers," He says and turns around. 
DeathStorm transforms and picks up Wolfgang in his talons, flying off toward 
the Alliance base.

"Let's get out of here," He says to Nemesis, FZ, and DevilDuer and flies off. 
FZ flies off after him and DevilDuer runs toward the base's direction.
